{"tid":592620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又來！？學會倡尖咀巴士總站變露天廣場","createTime":"2018-03-14T10:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T12:10:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e0874684273029c966e6969e1a22b1ba41fbed56","tid":592620,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"海濱事務委員會九龍、荃灣及葵青海濱發展專責小組明日(15日)開會，園境師學會建議，將尖沙咀天星碼頭巴士總站改建為露天廣場，該會提出以巴士站取代巴士總站，釋放更多空間予行人；<span style=\"color: red;\">拆走礙眼的建築物</span>，重新設計上蓋；加設座椅；放置古董巴士，反映集體回憶。<br />\n<br />\n園境師學會認為，現時該處大部分地面空間被巴士及其他車輛佔用，嚴重影響行人及海濱環境，建議把巴士總站變成富有地方特色及活力的廣場，希望得到海濱事務委員會支持，引導政府落實建議，改善海濱環境及其連貫性和可達性，為市民提供更舒適、安全及有地區特色的城市空間，帶出更多美好的集體回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180314/bkn-20180314174558778-0314_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180314%2Fbkn-20180314174558778-0314_00822_001.html&d=5EFcCi6GraevK3nzQ%2F85iW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=49a6d8d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180314/bkn-20180314174558778-0314_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ed15dc156faf6d609c2ecd4baf593801d91aa780","tid":592620,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拆走礙眼的建築物</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲"},{"pid":"babcd5073f95ba7fcf8fbf68dc3d057c715a9079","tid":592620,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"老貓你身為巴膠，點睇"},{"pid":"17a2ad524a39656b94337ae521b3610b4fb004f8","tid":592620,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"最撚礙眼就係支那蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852f9f8f7969a67acda9670f90341a0dc09c1b82","tid":592620,"uid":36441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"戇撚9 一定仲塞車"},{"pid":"16a241beb0b0525c6c149a4e1f6